476
00:45:41.568 --> 00:45:43.153
Ge hit den. Ge hit!

477
00:45:43.320 --> 00:45:44.613
Fem sekunder.

478
00:45:44.780 --> 00:45:46.990
Ge mig min choklad. Ge hit den!

479
